values: Who wants to join me?

We live in a world where my brother can accidentally wash his phone in with jeans on a Saturday, but via Amazon.com, have a brand new Nokia N95 on a Tuesday. I'm so jealous. I *wanted* that phone, when I replaced my 6600 with the CrackBerry.
According to Wikipedia, "Suzi Quatro's first single "Rolling Stone" was a flop everywhere except Portugal, where it made number one."
"This sign is red. If it appears blue, you are going way too fast."                                           -Anonymous
... this self-indulgent, time-defying, insomniac collection is mostly friends only.

A gathering point for all the things I intersect and find silly enough to centralize: Weight Watchers recipe cards from 1974 "There's a certain serve-it-at- your-next-key-party freakiness to a lot of these dishes."
As horrible as it sounds, I think the hurricane is lulling me to sleep...
